      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Central Committee of Sri Lanka Freedom Party (SLFP) has decided to back SLPP MP Dullas Alahapperuma in the parliamentary vote to elect a new President, party\u2019s general secretary MP Dayasiri Jayasekara says."
